 at least one match for their national team.\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Rugby union in Romania]]\n\n==External links==\n* {{in lang|ro}} [https://web.archive.org/web/20090929001108/http://www.dinamorugby.ro/ Dinamo Rugby Bucure\u0219ti official website]\n* {{in lang|ro}} [https://www.super-liga.ro/superliga/echipe/dinamo/ SuperLiga Squad Details]\n* {{in lang|en}} [http://www.itsrugby.co.uk/team-squad-dinamobucuresti.html itsrugby.co.uk Squad Details]\n* {{in lang|ro}} [http://www.planetaovala.ro/ PlanetaOvala.ro \u2013 Romanian Rugby News]\n\n{{SuperLiga (rugby)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dinamo, Bucuresti}}\n[[Category:CS Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti|Rugby union]]\n[[Category:Romanian rugby union teams]]\n[[Category:Rugby clubs established in 1948]]\n[[Category:1948 establishments in Romania]]\n", "text_old": "{{dablink|This article is about the rugby club. For the sports club, see [[CS Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti]]}}\n{{Infobox rugby team\n  | teamname    = Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti\n  | image       = Dinamo logo.jpg\n  | imagesize   = 200px\n  | fullname    = Clubul Sportiv Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti\n  | location    = [[Bucharest]], [[Romania]]\n  | countryflag = Romania\n  | founded     = 1948\n  | ground      = [[Stadionul Florea Dumitrache|Florea Dumitrache]]\n  | capacity    = 1,500\n  | president   = [[George Cosac]]\n  | coach       = [[Cosmin Ra\u021biu]]\n  | captain     = [[Tudorel Bratu]]\n  | league      = [[SuperLiga (rugby)|CEC Bank SuperLiga]]\n  | season      = [[2018\u201319 SuperLiga season|2018\u201319]]\n  | position    = 6th\n  | url         = http://www.csdinamo.eu/sectia-jocuri-sportive/rugby/\n}}\n\n{{CS Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti sections}}\n\n'''Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti''' is one of the top [[Rugby union|rugby]] clubs in [[Romania]]. Located in the nation\u2019s capital, [[Bucharest]], the Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti side traditionally consisted of members drawn from the ranks of the civil service and/or police. Along with the army side, Steaua, the Dinamo team is one of the nation\u2019s top rugby union outfits. The Dinamo Gaz Sud team, as they are presently known, won the 2007\u201308 Romanian top division (Divizia Nationala) title, defeating archrivals Steaua 6\u20130. This 2008 victory was the side's most recent success, with the team bowing out of the club competition at the semi-final stage during the past two seasons, most recently to eventual champions Baia Mare. Nevertheless, Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti has been the dominant club side in Romania since the arrival of the 21st century, recording six titles over the past decade. They currently play in the 2019-2020 season of the [[SuperLiga (rugby)|CEC Bank SuperLiga]], the first division of Romanian rugby. \n\n== Rivalries ==\n==='''CSA Steaua Bucure\u0219ti'''=== \nBoth CS Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti and [[CSA Steaua Bucure\u0219ti (rugby)|CSA Steaua Bucure\u0219ti]] have been bitter rivals in most sports since 1949, and when it comes to rugby, both sides are always competitive about who is the better team of Bucharest.\n\n==Achievements==\n\n=== Domestic ===\n*'''[[SuperLiga (rugby)|Divizia Na\u021bional\u0103]]'''\n**'''Winners (16):''' 1951, 1952, 1956, 1965, 1969, 1982, 1991, 1994, 1996, 1998, 2000, 2001, 2002, 2004, 2007, 2008\n*'''Cupa Rom\u00e2niei''' '''\n**'''Winners (12):''' 1954, 1959, 1980, 1989, 1996, 1997, 1998, 2000, 2001, 2002, 2004, 2008\n\n=== European ===\n*'''Champions League (rugby)'''\n**'''Winners (1):''' 1967\n\n== Current squad ==\n{{Rugby squad start}} \n{{rugby squad player | nat=GEO | pos=HK | name=Merab Matkava}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=RSA | pos=HK | name=Samuel Jay Swanepoel}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=ROU | pos=PR | name=Daniel Bumbac}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=ROU | pos=PR | name=Drago\u0219 Dumitrescu}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=ROU | pos=PR | name=Andrei Lungu}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=ROU | pos=PR | name='''[[Cosmin Manole]]'''}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=ROU | pos=PR | name=Florin M\u0103tu\u0219a}}\n{{rugby squad player | nat=ARG | pos=PR | n